OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FThe US has imposed sanctions on Cuban
OL,7,FPresident Miguel Diaz-Canel, his wife
OL,8,Fand three other people, in the latest
OL,9,Fmove by the Trump administration to
OL,10,Fincrease pressure on Cuba's leadership.
OL,12,FIncluded in the sanctions on Thursday
OL,13,Fare Alejandro Castro Espin, the son of
OL,14,Fformer Cuban President Raul Castro and
OL,15,FVilma Espin.
OL,17,FHe previously served as an adviser to
OL,18,FCuba's Defence and National Security
OL,19,FCommission and was present when Raul
OL,20,FCastro met then-US President Barack
OL,21,FObama in Havana in 2016.
OL,26,@oD@SrtuD@YrtvD@ZrzwD@Jrt{D@crz
