OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FHis son, Raul Alejandro Castro Calis,
OL,7,Fwas also listed.
OL,9,FThe measures come as US President
OL,10,FDonald Trump continues to intensify
OL,11,Fpressure on Cuba, including threats of
OL,12,Fmilitary action after the removal of
OL,13,FVenezuelan leader Nicolas Maduro in
OL,14,FJanuary and the introduction of an
OL,15,Fenergy blockade that has cut off fuel
OL,16,Fsupplies to the island.
OL,18,FThe energy blockade has led to severe
OL,19,Fblackouts, food shortages and a
OL,20,Fworsening economic crisis across Cuba.
OL,26,@nD@LrzuD@Xrp
