OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780686673
OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FThe threats became more prominent
OL,7,Fafter the US announced criminal
OL,8,Fcharges against Raul Castro last month.
OL,10,FThursday's penalties follow an
OL,11,Fexecutive order signed by Trump
OL,12,Fexpanding sanctions against Cuba,
OL,13,Ffreezing individuals' property and
OL,14,Fbank accounts in the US, although it
OL,15,Fis unclear how closely those targeted
OL,16,Fare tied to the US financial system.
OL,26,@pD@Srz
