OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780686673
OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FRichard Feinberg, former US national
OL,7,Fsecurity adviser on Latin America and
OL,8,Fprofessor emeritus of international
OL,9,Fpolitical economy at the University of
OL,10,FCalifornia, San Diego, said it is
OL,11,F"pretty unlikely" that Cuba's
OL,12,Fpresident and others have assets in
OL,13,Fthe US.
OL,15,FHe added that the sanctions "could be
OL,16,Fseen as preliminary to an intervention
OL,17,For increasing pressure on the regime
OL,18,Fto cut a deal," adding that the
OL,19,Frhetoric from Trump and US Secretary
OL,20,Fof State Marco Rubio "could take you
OL,21,Fin either direction".
