OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FMiguel Diaz-Canel accused Trump of
OL,7,Fmaking "new threatening statements
OL,8,Fagainst Cuba" and said the measures
OL,9,Fwere aimed at reinforcing the blockade
OL,10,Fand escalating tensions between Cuba
OL,11,Fand the US.
OL,13,F"This political blindness adds to the
OL,14,Fcoercive measures applied in recent
OL,15,Fweeks against our country, designed to
OL,16,Fharm the Cuban people," he wrote on X.
OL,26,@nD@IrtoD@HOUpD@MO]uD@AOUxD@WO]
