OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,F"The aggression and perversion of the
OL,7,FUS government will clash with our
OL,8,Fresolve to confront the worst-case
OL,9,Fscenarios and resist the imperial
OL,10,Fonslaught."
OL,12,FAsked on Thursday if his sanctions
OL,13,Fwere meant to accelerate Cuba's
OL,14,Fcollapse, Trump said: "We just want
OL,15,Fthem to be a nicely run country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]vD@WOU
