OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780686673
OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,F"The country is starving and it's got
OL,7,Fno energy, it's got no oil, it's got
OL,8,Fno money, it's got nothing. It's got a
OL,9,Fbeautiful piece of land. You could
OL,10,Fhave beautiful resorts," Trump told
OL,11,Freporters at an unrelated event in the
OL,12,FOval Office.
OL,14,FAsked whether Cuba is close to
OL,15,Fcollapsing, he said, "It's sort of
OL,16,Fcollapsed" and added that "we're going
OL,17,Fto handle that as soon as we've
OL,18,Ffinished" military operations in Iran.
OL,20,F"I like to do one thing at a time,"
OL,21,FTrump said.
