OL,3,CUS sanctions Cuban president in latest
OL,4,Cmove to pressure island
OL,6,FRubio, the son of Cuban immigrants who
OL,7,Fhas taken a stance against Cuba's
OL,8,Fsocialist leadership, has said Trump's
OL,9,Fpreference is to reach a deal but has
OL,10,Fsaid he is doubtful the US can find a
OL,11,Fdiplomatic resolution with the current
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FThose "designated today direct or fund
OL,15,Fthe regime and its efforts to mobilise
OL,16,Fits radical revolutionary movements in
OL,17,Fthe United States and around the
OL,18,Fworld," Rubio said in a statement.
