OL,6,FRubio has defended the Trump
OL,7,Fadministration's decision to slap
OL,8,Fescalating sanctions on Havana, the
OL,9,Flargest of which is against Grupo de
OL,10,FAdministracion Empresarial S.A, a
OL,11,Fbusiness conglomerate operated by the
OL,12,FCuban Revolutionary Armed Forces.
